{"tid":1214411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解決生理鹽水物資短缺問題","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:20:43.000Z","uid":180719,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e25f1182f51a3c97973a576fd5ac63231221fd8c","tid":1214411,"uid":180719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"其實中左胡椒噴霧係應該用溝左baby shampoo嘅水沖左先用清水或生理鹽水沖<br />\n因為胡椒噴霧係油性 想像下就咁用水洗個煮完餸嘅煎pan都好難 所以一定要落番梘 而baby shampoo比較溫和<br />\n咁樣清理胡椒噴霧會有效好多同埋唔洗嘥咁多生理鹽水 尋日見啲人一兩個人就用晒成支<br />\n希望大家買物資除左買鹽水 要<span style=\"color: red;\">買埋baby shampoo</span><br />\n<br />\n另外建議大家用呢個嘴嘅樽去入定baby shampoo溝水<br />\n比例: 大概唧3-4下baby shampoo溝一支清水 (唔係食水都得 所以建議喺屋企入定水)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Viz1LtO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViz1LtO.png&h=8061b4a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cca9ad9e9f22d53fbca660966aac7be058cbb6de","tid":1214411,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"19f92e8c03b2021a9a9c97557bcf95adbe8d3782","tid":1214411,"uid":211803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f85dd4148c45799b3a6dc4329f364234480aec38","tid":1214411,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"push"}]}